/uploads/original/0/8273/3449830-7994219330-FpaPUHlXEAMvnBl.jpg\"><img alt=\"No Caption Provided\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449830-7994219330-FpaPUHlXEAMvnBl.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449830-7994219330-FpaPUHlXEAMvnBl.jpg 1080w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449830-7994219330-FpaPUHlXEAMvnBl.jpg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-width=\"1920\"></a></figure><h2>Activities</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/the-gb-album-club-025-untrue-by-burial-1909981/\"><strong>The GB Album Club 025 - Untrue By Burial</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/unclejam23/\">@unclejam23</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449606-2472541590-FpnSWLYaMAAcK2r.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449606\" data-ratio=\"0.5247619047619\" data-width=\"3150\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 3150px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449606-2472541590-FpnSWLYaMAAcK2r.jpg\"><img alt=\"Let's talk about dubstep!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449606-2472541590-FpnSWLYaMAAcK2r.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449606-2472541590-FpnSWLYaMAAcK2r.jpg 3150w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449606-2472541590-FpnSWLYaMAAcK2r.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449606-2472541590-FpnSWLYaMAAcK2r.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449606-2472541590-FpnSWLYaMAAcK2r.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Let's talk about dubstep!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Untrue by Burial is the latest pick by the Giant Bomb Community Album Club! If you have thoughts about this universally acclaimed electronic album and how it influenced the dubstep genre, share them by clicking the link above!</p><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/coffee-talk/3030-73092/forums/coffee-talk-is-the-4th-game-of-the-uugpgc-year-2-f-1909806/\">Coffee Talk Is The 4th Game Of The UUGPGC Year 2! Finish By February 27! All Are Welcome. Please Mark Spoilers!</a></strong>(By:<a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/bigsocrates/\">@bigsocrates</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449839-5213206447-Fp0-nYyakAIoroa.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449839\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1920\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1920px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449839-5213206447-Fp0-nYyakAIoroa.jpg\"><img alt=\"Let's talk about cyber elfs!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449839-5213206447-Fp0-nYyakAIoroa.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449839-5213206447-Fp0-nYyakAIoroa.jpg 1920w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449839-5213206447-Fp0-nYyakAIoroa.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449839-5213206447-Fp0-nYyakAIoroa.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449839-5213206447-Fp0-nYyakAIoroa.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Let's talk about cyber elfs!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Don't forget <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/coffee-talk/3030-73092/\">Coffee Talk</a> is the 4th game selected for the Community Game Pass Game Club! If you have any non-spoiler impressions of the game, its structure, and general aesthetic choices, feel free to share them!</p><h2>Blogs</h2><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/borgmaster/blog/all-ps1-games-in-order-part-019/269383/\">All PS1 Games In Order: Part 019</a> +</strong></p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/3do/3045-26/forums/all-3do-games-kinda-in-order-1993-part-2-1910045/\"><strong>All 3DO Games (Kinda) In Order: 1993 (Part 2)</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/borgmaster/\">@borgmaster</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449607-2376111236-FpxDNRragAYKary.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449607\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-width=\"960\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 960px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449607-2376111236-FpxDNRragAYKary.jpg\"><img alt=\"You MUST click the link to this blog and listen to the theme music borgmaster encountered while playing this game.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449607-2376111236-FpxDNRragAYKary.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449607-2376111236-FpxDNRragAYKary.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449607-2376111236-FpxDNRragAYKary.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449607-2376111236-FpxDNRragAYKary.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>You MUST click the link to this blog and listen to the theme music borgmaster encountered while playing this game.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">borgmaster has a new entry to their series where they look at every single PS1 game by NA release date! This week, they talk about <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/rise-2-resurrection/3030-16110/\">Rise 2: Resurrection</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/nba-live-96/3030-20257/\">NBA Live 96</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/nba-shootout/3030-21747/\">NBA ShootOut</a>, and Panzer General!</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">More importantly, it's time for more 3DO goodness from borgmaster! This week they check out games like Putt-Putt Joins the Parade and <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/shelley-duvalls-its-a-birds-life/3030-48845/\">Shelley Duvall's It's a Bird's Life</a>! Did you know Shelley Duvall did an educational 3DO game about birds?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/super-luckys-tale/3030-59901/forums/indie-game-of-the-week-308-new-super-luckys-tale-1910053/\"><strong>Indie Game of the Week 308: New Super Lucky's Tale</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/mento/\">@mento</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Mento tackles <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/super-luckys-tale/3030-59901/\">Super Lucky's Tale</a> for their latest \"Indie Game of the Week\" and they judge the game and asses its attempts to \"get the genre right\" are enough to keep the series afloat outside the context of VR.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/history-is-no-game-part-2-the-oregon-trail-and-whe-1909963/\"><strong>History is No Game Part 2 -- \"The Oregon Trail\" and \"When Rivers Were Trails\"</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/bladeofcreation/\">@bladeofcreation</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449837-3082857462-34496.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449837\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1920\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1920px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449837-3082857462-34496.png\"><img alt=\"Is this franchise still alive? Does it make sense outside of the world of VR?\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449837-3082857462-34496.png\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449837-3082857462-34496.png 1920w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449837-3082857462-34496.png 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449837-3082857462-34496.png 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449837-3082857462-34496.png 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Is this franchise still alive? Does it make sense outside of the world of VR?</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">BladeOfCreation has a new edition of their blog series where they look at games that tackle historical subjects! This time, they discuss the enduring legacy of <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/the-oregon-trail/3030-17852/\">The Oregon Trail</a> and what <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/when-rivers-were-trails/3030-76954/\">When Rivers Were Trails</a> does to fix that.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/jeremyf/blog/rest-of-the-snes-februarys-backog-battle/269380/\"><strong>Rest Of The SNES: February's Backog Battle</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/jeremyf/\">@jeremyf</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">jeremyf dusted off the Super NES Classic Edition and reviewed most of the games on it with their latest blog on the site! If you want to read how games like <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/f-zero/3030-15242/\">F-Zero</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/super-mario-kart/3030-19071/\">Super Mario Kart</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/super-punch-out/3030-6029/\">Super Punch-Out!!</a> fare on the device, click the link above!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/jeffrud/blog/hucartography-v-youkai-douchuuki-and-the-arrival-o/269402/\"><strong>HuCARTography V: Youkai Douchuuki And The Arrival Of Third Parties</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/jeffrud/\">@jeffrud</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449613-8844808710-FpiAvo3aQAYQ2Cz.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449613\" data-ratio=\"0.56117021276596\" data-width=\"2256\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 2256px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449613-8844808710-FpiAvo3aQAYQ2Cz.png\"><img alt=\"Another highly educational and reflective blog from BladeOfCreation.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449613-8844808710-FpiAvo3aQAYQ2Cz.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449613-8844808710-FpiAvo3aQAYQ2Cz.png 2256w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449613-8844808710-FpiAvo3aQAYQ2Cz.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449613-8844808710-FpiAvo3aQAYQ2Cz.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449613-8844808710-FpiAvo3aQAYQ2Cz.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Another highly educational and reflective blog from BladeOfCreation.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">jeffrud returns with another blog about the <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/turbografx-16/3045-55/\">TurboGrafx-16</a>/PC Engine and why it deserves the respect of gamers both young and old. This week, they checked out Yokai Dochuki, a game that details a young boy trying to get out of Hell.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/quest-for-the-worst-adventure-game-special-lets-ta-1910046/\"><strong>Quest For The Worst Adventure Game SPECIAL: Let's Talk About Every Free Adventure Game On GOG (Part 1: The Modern Games)</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/zombiepie/\">@zombiepie</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">ZombiePie is doing a mini-series that looks at every single free adventure game in GOG's \"Free Games Collection!\" This week they checked out modern\" titles like <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/delores-a-thimbleweed-park-mini-adventure/3030-78503/\">Delores: A Thimbleweed Park Mini-Adventure</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/samorost/3030-12860/\">Samorost</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/cayne-a-stasis-story/3030-57889/\">Cayne: A Stasis Story</a>, and MORE!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/infantpipoc/blog/2006-year-of-first-contacts-between-sworn-enemies/269410/\"><strong>2006: Year of First Contacts Between “Sworn Enemies”</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/infantpipoc/\">@infantpipoc</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449535-1.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449535\" data-ratio=\"0.42647058823529\" data-width=\"1224\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1224px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449535-1.png\"><img alt=\"GOG isn't exactly known for the impressive rotation of games they give to you for free, but there are some gems!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449535-1.png\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449535-1.png 1224w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449535-1.png 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449535-1.png 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449535-1.png 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>GOG isn't exactly known for the impressive rotation of games they give to you for free, but there are some gems!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">infantpipoc continues their book review blog series with an assessment of The Three-Body Problem! Is there a reason why it is one of the most successful Chinese sci-fi novels of all time? What can games and movies learn from it?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/nuclear-throne/3030-41999/forums/whats-the-greatest-video-game-nuclear-throne-1910038/\"><strong>What's the Greatest Video Game: Nuclear Throne</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/imunbeatable80/\">@imunbeatable80</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">For their latest \"What's the Greatest Video Game\" blog, imunbeatable80 ended up playing <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/nuclear-throne/3030-41999/\">Nuclear Throne</a>! Did they end up enjoying its procedurally generated rogue-like action gameplay?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/gamer_152/blog/transit-art-in-off-peak/269331/\"><strong>Transit: Art in Off-Peak</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/gamer_152/\">@gamer_152</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449838\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1280\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1280px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg\"><img alt=\"Are the works of Cosmo D subversive art? You tell me!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg 1280w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" data-width=\"960\"></a><figcaption>Are the works of Cosmo D subversive art? You tell me!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Moderator Gamer_152 examined <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/off-peak/3030-55396/\">Off-Peak</a> from developer <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/cosmo-d/3010-14796/\">Cosmo D</a> and discusses why the game, despite its bizarre visuals and in-game tasks, stands as an autobiographical environment for New York City and the modern art scene.</p><h2>Discussion Threads</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/wo-long-fallen-dynasty/3030-86455/forums/new-wo-long-demo-is-out-lets-you-carry-progress-to-1910047/\"><strong>New \"Wo Long\" Demo Is Out, Lets You Carry Progress To Main Game</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/atheistpreacher/\">@atheistpreacher</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449835-9772492878-Fp1BUeEakAE8PWs.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449835\" data-ratio=\"0.525\" data-width=\"1200\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1200px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449835-9772492878-Fp1BUeEakAE8PWs.jpg\"><img alt=\"Anyone give this demo a try?\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449835-9772492878-Fp1BUeEakAE8PWs.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449835-9772492878-Fp1BUeEakAE8PWs.jpg 1200w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449835-9772492878-Fp1BUeEakAE8PWs.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449835-9772492878-Fp1BUeEakAE8PWs.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449835-9772492878-Fp1BUeEakAE8PWs.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Anyone give this demo a try?</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">How many of you have checked out the demo for <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/wo-long-fallen-dynasty/3030-86455/\">Wo Long: Fallen Dynasty</a>? Is providing a demo that lets you carry over your progress for the release version the new normal? How do you think the game itself feels?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/the-concessions-start-rolling-microsoft-agrees-to--1909962/\"><strong>The Concessions Start Rolling - Microsoft Agrees To Bring Call Of Duty To Nintendo Platforms For 10 Years</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/zombiepie/\">@zombiepie</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3173169\" data-ratio=\"0.62135416666667\" data-width=\"1920\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1920px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV\"><img alt=\"Is Call of Duty really worth fighting over these days?\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV 1920w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Is Call of Duty really worth fighting over these days?</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Microsoft has an agreement to bring \"Xbox games and Activision titles\" to Nintendo platforms for at least ten years. Is this enough to abate regulators? What do you think they mean by \"Xbox games?\" Join the community discussion with your thoughts!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/mortal-kombat-12/3030-88562/forums/mortal-kombat-12-announced-1910014/\"><strong>Mortal Kombat 12 Announced</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/kevinwalsh/\">@kevinwalsh</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">What does everyone make of the <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/mortal-kombat-12/3030-88562/\">Mortal Kombat 12</a> announcement? Are you excited? Are you disappointed it isn't Injustice 3? Is Ed Boon still gaming's most lovable troll? Share your take on all of these questions by clicking the link above</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/atomic-heart/3030-68449/forums/aftershock-atomic-heart-impressions-1909982/\"><strong>Atomic Heart Impressions Sharing Thread</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/spacemanspiff00/\">@spacemanspiff00</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449836\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"2560\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 2560px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg\"><img alt=\"Is this game too thirsty? Join the conversation!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg 2560w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Is this game too thirsty? Join the conversation!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">How many of y'all have given <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/atomic-heart/3030-68449/\">Atomic Heart</a> a shot? What do you make of its bite-sized campaign or its mix of adventure exploration and first-person shooting? Here's a link to the community discussion thread!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/bethesda-announces-mighty-doom-1909971/\"><strong>Bethesda Announces Mighty Doom</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/rorie/\">@rorie</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Bethesda announced Mighty Doom and people are still divided about its style and genre. What is your reaction to the Doom spin-off? Are you down to play a top-down Doom with a cutesy art style?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/your-wish-list-of-classic-games-to-have-remake-or--1909983/\"><strong>Your Wish List Of Classic Games To Have Remake Or Remastered Ports?</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/gtxforza/\">@gtxforza</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449834\" data-ratio=\"0.2641056422569\" data-width=\"833\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 833px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.png\"><img alt=\"This is maybe the comment of the week if you ask me.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.png 833w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>This is maybe the comment of the week if you ask me.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">With the <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/resident-evil-4/3030-86329/\">Resident Evil 4</a> remake looking better by the minute and rumors about a remaster of Snake Eater continuing to swell, what games that still have not gotten the remake treatment are you holding out for these days?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/microsoft-and-call-of-dutyam-i-missing-something-1910006/\"><strong>Microsoft And Call Of Duty... Am I Missing Something?</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/topcyclist/\">@topcyclist</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">We have a discussion thread on the forums debating if <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/call-of-duty/3025-82/\">Call of Duty</a> is as big as Sony and anti-trust advocates are claiming? Is the franchise still the multiplayer monolith it once was? This comment seems pretty on point.</p><h2>Lists</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/captainofthestars/lists/beyond-my-reach/374219/\"><strong>Beyond My Reach</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/captainofthestars/\">@captainofthestars</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449841\" data-ratio=\"0.59949937421777\" data-width=\"799\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 799px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png\"><img alt=\"I think we all have a list like this one in us! Keep me updated if you actually make one.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png 799w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 799px) 100vw, 799px\" data-width=\"799\"></a><figcaption>I think we all have a list like this one in us! Keep me updated if you actually make one.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">captainofthestars has made a list of games they desperately want to play but don't know how they will make that possible as copies are hard to come by. Give their list a read and think about making your own if you can relate.</p><h2>User Reviews</h2><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449840\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-width=\"640\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 640px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg\"><img alt=\"I don't think you are getting breaking coverage of Grabbed by the Ghoulies other than from the Giant Bomb community.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg 640w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>I don't think you are getting breaking coverage of Grabbed by the Ghoulies other than from the Giant Bomb community.</figcaption></figure><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/infantpipoc/\">@infantpipoc</a> decided to go back to the MGS game that sold them on the franchise: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/metal-gear-solid-2-sons-of-liberty/3030-12388/user-reviews/2200-32227/\"><strong>Metal Gear Solid 2: Sons of Liberty</strong></a> under the backdrop of all of the talk about a possible Snake Eater remake.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/toolzz360/\">@toolzz360</a> has been going through Rare Replay and when they got to <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/grabbed-by-the-ghoulies/3030-1484/user-reviews/2200-32226/\"><strong>Grabbed by the Ghoulies</strong></a>, they felt inspired to write a review for the game where you can read why they think Rare's first post-Microsoft purchase outing wasn't a success.</p><h2>Wiki Of The Week</h2><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/banjo-kazooie-nuts-bolts/3030-20586/\">Banjo-Kazooie: Nuts &amp; Bolts</a></strong></p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-2437013\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1280\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1280px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg\"><img alt=\"Considering how popular crafting games are these days, how far off was Nuts &amp; Bolts to stardom?\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg 1280w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Considering how popular crafting games are these days, how far off was Nuts &amp; Bolts to stardom?</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Earlier in the week, Wikipedia made Banjo-Kazooie: Nuts &amp; Bolts their \"featured article\" of the day, but did you know that the Giant Bomb wiki page for the game is just as impressive as Wikipedia's? Click the link below to see what I mean!</p> ]]>",
