k Mini-Adventure</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/samorost/3030-12860/\">Samorost</a>, <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/cayne-a-stasis-story/3030-57889/\">Cayne: A Stasis Story</a>, and MORE!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/infantpipoc/blog/2006-year-of-first-contacts-between-sworn-enemies/269410/\"><strong>2006: Year of First Contacts Between “Sworn Enemies”</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/infantpipoc/\">@infantpipoc</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449535-1.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449535\" data-ratio=\"0.42647058823529\" data-width=\"1224\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1224px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449535-1.png\"><img alt=\"GOG isn't exactly known for the impressive rotation of games they give to you for free, but there are some gems!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449535-1.png\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449535-1.png 1224w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449535-1.png 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449535-1.png 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449535-1.png 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>GOG isn't exactly known for the impressive rotation of games they give to you for free, but there are some gems!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">infantpipoc continues their book review blog series with an assessment of The Three-Body Problem! Is there a reason why it is one of the most successful Chinese sci-fi novels of all time? What can games and movies learn from it?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/nuclear-throne/3030-41999/forums/whats-the-greatest-video-game-nuclear-throne-1910038/\"><strong>What's the Greatest Video Game: Nuclear Throne</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/imunbeatable80/\">@imunbeatable80</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">For their latest \"What's the Greatest Video Game\" blog, imunbeatable80 ended up playing <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/nuclear-throne/3030-41999/\">Nuclear Throne</a>! Did they end up enjoying its procedurally generated rogue-like action gameplay?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/gamer_152/blog/transit-art-in-off-peak/269331/\"><strong>Transit: Art in Off-Peak</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/gamer_152/\">@gamer_152</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449838\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1280\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1280px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg\"><img alt=\"Are the works of Cosmo D subversive art? You tell me!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg 1280w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449838-5725991723-ss_88.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" data-width=\"960\"></a><figcaption>Are the works of Cosmo D subversive art? You tell me!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Moderator Gamer_152 examined <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/off-peak/3030-55396/\">Off-Peak</a> from developer <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/cosmo-d/3010-14796/\">Cosmo D</a> and discusses why the game, despite its bizarre visuals and in-game tasks, stands as an autobiographical environment for New York City a