ndo Platforms For 10 Years</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/zombiepie/\">@zombiepie</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3173169\" data-ratio=\"0.62135416666667\" data-width=\"1920\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1920px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV\"><img alt=\"Is Call of Duty really worth fighting over these days?\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV 1920w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/25/250401/3173169-6160596313-ESrowJNVAAkU1qV 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Is Call of Duty really worth fighting over these days?</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Microsoft has an agreement to bring \"Xbox games and Activision titles\" to Nintendo platforms for at least ten years. Is this enough to abate regulators? What do you think they mean by \"Xbox games?\" Join the community discussion with your thoughts!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/mortal-kombat-12/3030-88562/forums/mortal-kombat-12-announced-1910014/\"><strong>Mortal Kombat 12 Announced</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/kevinwalsh/\">@kevinwalsh</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">What does everyone make of the <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/mortal-kombat-12/3030-88562/\">Mortal Kombat 12</a> announcement? Are you excited? Are you disappointed it isn't Injustice 3? Is Ed Boon still gaming's most lovable troll? Share your take on all of these questions by clicking the link above</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/atomic-heart/3030-68449/forums/aftershock-atomic-heart-impressions-1909982/\"><strong>Atomic Heart Impressions Sharing Thread</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/spacemanspiff00/\">@spacemanspiff00</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449836\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"2560\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 2560px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg\"><img alt=\"Is this game too thirsty? Join the conversation!\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg 2560w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449836-3932181715-cover.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Is this game too thirsty? Join the conversation!</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">How many of y'all have given <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/atomic-heart/3030-68449/\">Atomic Heart</a> a shot? What do you make of its bite-sized campaign or its mix of adventure exploration and first-person shooting? Here's a link to the community discussion thread!</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/bethesda-announces-mighty-doom-1909971/\"><strong>Bethesda Announces Mighty Doom</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/rorie/\">@rorie</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Bethesda announced Mighty Doom and people are still divided about its style and genre. What is your reaction to the Doom spin-off? Are you down to play a top-down Doom with a cutesy art style?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/your-wish-list-of-classic-games-to-have-remake-or--1909983/\"><strong>Your Wish List Of Classic Games To Have Remake Or Remastered Ports?</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/gtxforza/\">@gtxforza</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449834\" data-ratio=\"0.2641056422569\" data-width=\"833\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 833px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.png\"><img alt=\"This is maybe the comment of the week if you ask me.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.png 833w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449834-6442337833-Fp1DoNCacAA0xGf.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>This is maybe the comment of the week if you ask me.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">With the <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/resident-evil-4/3030-86329/\">Resident Evil 4</a> remake looking better by the minute and rumors about a remaster of Snake Eater continuing to swell, what games that still have not gotten the remake treatment are you holding out for these days?</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/forums/general-discussion-30/microsoft-and-call-of-dutyam-i-missing-something-1910006/\"><strong>Microsoft And Call Of Duty... Am I Missing Something?</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/topcyclist/\">@topcyclist</a>)</p><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">We have a discussion thread on the forums debating if <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/call-of-duty/3025-82/\">Call of Duty</a> is as big as Sony and anti-trust advocates are claiming? Is the franchise still the multiplayer monolith it once was? This comment seems pretty on point.</p><h2>Lists</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/captainofthestars/lists/beyond-my-reach/374219/\"><strong>Beyond My Reach</strong></a> (By: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/captainofthestars/\">@captainofthestars</a>)</p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449841\" data-ratio=\"0.59949937421777\" data-width=\"799\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 799px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png\"><img alt=\"I think we all have a list like this one in us! Keep me updated if you actually make one.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png 799w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449841-6807030606-FpsSUlMaMAEgb7F.png 480w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 799px) 100vw, 799px\" data-width=\"799\"></a><figcaption>I think we all have a list like this one in us! Keep me updated if you actually make one.</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">captainofthestars has made a list of games they desperately want to play but don't know how they will make that possible as copies are hard to come by. Give their list a read and think about making your own if you can relate.</p><h2>User Reviews</h2><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-3449840\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-width=\"640\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 640px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg\"><img alt=\"I don't think you are getting breaking coverage of Grabbed by the Ghoulies other than from the Giant Bomb community.\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg 640w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/0/8273/3449840-8268468605-FpXSLbbagAAcdi-.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>I don't think you are getting breaking coverage of Grabbed by the Ghoulies other than from the Giant Bomb community.</figcaption></figure><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/infantpipoc/\">@infantpipoc</a> decided to go back to the MGS game that sold them on the franchise: <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/metal-gear-solid-2-sons-of-liberty/3030-12388/user-reviews/2200-32227/\"><strong>Metal Gear Solid 2: Sons of Liberty</strong></a> under the backdrop of all of the talk about a possible Snake Eater remake.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/profile/toolzz360/\">@toolzz360</a> has been going through Rare Replay and when they got to <a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/grabbed-by-the-ghoulies/3030-1484/user-reviews/2200-32226/\"><strong>Grabbed by the Ghoulies</strong></a>, they felt inspired to write a review for the game where you can read why they think Rare's first post-Microsoft purchase outing wasn't a success.</p><h2>Wiki Of The Week</h2><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/banjo-kazooie-nuts-bolts/3030-20586/\">Banjo-Kazooie: Nuts &amp; Bolts</a></strong></p><figure data-align=\"right\" data-size=\"small\" data-img-src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg\" data-ref-id=\"1300-2437013\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-width=\"1280\" data-embed-type=\"image\" style=\"width: 1280px\"><a href=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg\"><img alt=\"Considering how popular crafting games are these days, how far off was Nuts &amp; Bolts to stardom?\" src=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/original/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg 1280w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_super/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg 960w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_medium/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg 480w, https://www.giantbomb.com/a/uploads/scale_small/8/82063/2437013-nuts%26boltspic3.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" data-width=\"320\"></a><figcaption>Considering how popular crafting games are these days, how far off was Nuts &amp; Bolts to stardom?</figcaption></figure><p data-right-indent=\"0\" style=\"margin-left: 30px;\">Earlier in the week, Wikipedia made Banjo-Kazooie: Nuts &amp; Bolts their \"featured article\" of the day, but did you know that the Giant Bomb wiki page for the game is just as impressive as Wikipedia's? Click the link below to see what I mean!</p> ]]>",
